{
  "stem": "14251.5",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So now I was in this room with some other language.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And these kids were defiant and said that I was German, and all the people had been killed by the Germans.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This was when I first started to get some kind of a feeling about what really had happened.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My mother had told me, two days before the Russians came in that little sharecropper's hut, what was with us, who we were, what did it mean.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I didn't understand a word she said.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It seemed outrageous.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In other words, because people are something else, they had to be killed?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "What was this?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It made no sense.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I didn't even know what killed meant, let alone religion.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "What do you mean religion?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We look like the other people.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "What is it?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I knew all that by then.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I knew this was a Jewish orphanage.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I knew their parents had gotten killed.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I had learned a lot in that time.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I knew the people in the camps were Germans who hated us.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And my mother had been asked to spy on the other prisoners there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Turn in ten Nazis a-- a-- a week, and we'll give you a cabbage and you'll get to live in grand style.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But she wouldn't do it because her ethics said, I don't know these people.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Mm-mm.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Couldn't tell you.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It changed.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Don't know that either.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I just know we had-- we all had our heads shaved because of the lice, the bed bugs.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I had one little girl who must have felt sorry for me.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Her name was Zippella, which means in Yiddish little-- like corner, you know?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "If you had a cover like a pillowcase, this is the zippella in Yiddish.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
